title: #2114 - Zack Snyder
description: Listen to this episode from The Joe Rogan Experience on Spotify. Zack Snyder is a filmmaker, producer, and screenwriter known for films like "Justice League," "300," and "Army of the Dead." His latest film, "Rebel Moon - Part One: A Child of Fire," is now available on Netflix.
